Remind SLICE of Stakeholder Approval Inactivity
1.	Navigate here to create a new record: https://cmudev01.service-now.com/nav_to.do?uri=%2Fx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications.do%3Fsys_id%3D-1%26sys_is_list%3Dtrue%26sys_target%3Dx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications%26sysparm_checked_items%3D%26sysparm_fixed_query%3D%26sysparm_group_sort%3D%26sysparm_list_css%3D%26sysparm_query%3D%26sysparm_referring_url%3Dx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications_list.do%253fsysparm_clear_stack%253dtrue%26sysparm_target%3D%26sysparm_view%3D
2.	Fill out the mandatory fields on the record.
3.	Add an approval group for the Approvers
4.	Click the submit UI Action
5.	Click the Send for Stakeholder Approval UI Action
6.	Wait until the next 8AM after 72 hours of inactivity for the approval reminder to SLICE to fire. (The job runs at 8AM daily to check the approvals)
7.	As an Admin visit the outbox: https://cmudev01.service-now.com/nav_to.do?uri=%2Fsys_email_list.do%3Fsysparm_userpref_module%3D0271bb720a0a0b610089873ececf22c4%26sysparm_view%3Doutbox%26sysparm_query%3Dmailbox%3Doutbox%5Esys_created_onONToday@javascript:gs.daysAgoStart(0)@javascript:gs.daysAgoEnd(0)%5EEQ%26sysparm_clear_stack%3Dtrue
8.	Find the notification in the mailbox to the SLICE group with the subject: ${sysapproval.number} - Application for ${sysapproval.short_description} has pending approvals

Remind SLICE of Dean Approval Inactivity
1.	Navigate here to create a new record: https://cmudev01.service-now.com/nav_to.do?uri=%2Fx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications.do%3Fsys_id%3D-1%26sys_is_list%3Dtrue%26sys_target%3Dx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications%26sysparm_checked_items%3D%26sysparm_fixed_query%3D%26sysparm_group_sort%3D%26sysparm_list_css%3D%26sysparm_query%3D%26sysparm_referring_url%3Dx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications_list.do%253fsysparm_clear_stack%253dtrue%26sysparm_target%3D%26sysparm_view%3D
2.	Fill out the mandatory fields on the record.
3.	Add an approval group for the Approvers
4.	Click the submit UI Action
5.	Click the status field and change to Dean of Students Approval
6.	Click the save UI Action
7.	Wait until the next 8AM after 72 hours of inactivity for the approval reminder to SLICE to fire. (The job runs at 8AM daily to check the approvals)
8.	As an Admin visit the outbox: https://cmudev01.service-now.com/nav_to.do?uri=%2Fsys_email_list.do%3Fsysparm_userpref_module%3D0271bb720a0a0b610089873ececf22c4%26sysparm_view%3Doutbox%26sysparm_query%3Dmailbox%3Doutbox%5Esys_created_onONToday@javascript:gs.daysAgoStart(0)@javascript:gs.daysAgoEnd(0)%5EEQ%26sysparm_clear_stack%3Dtrue
9.	Find the notification in the mailbox to the SLICE group with the subject: ${sysapproval.number} - Application for ${sysapproval.short_description} has pending approvals

Remind SLICE of Stakeholder Approval Inactivity (set the timer to 31 minutes rather than 31 days)
1.	Navigate here to create a new record: https://cmudev01.service-now.com/nav_to.do?uri=%2Fx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications.do%3Fsys_id%3D-1%26sys_is_list%3Dtrue%26sys_target%3Dx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications%26sysparm_checked_items%3D%26sysparm_fixed_query%3D%26sysparm_group_sort%3D%26sysparm_list_css%3D%26sysparm_query%3D%26sysparm_referring_url%3Dx_camu_cmu_install_installation_applications_list.do%253fsysparm_clear_stack%253dtrue%26sysparm_target%3D%26sysparm_view%3D
2.	Fill out the mandatory fields on the record.
3.	Save the record.
4.	Click the status field and set the status to ‘Draft’
5.	Navigate to the outbox: https://cmudev01.service-now.com/nav_to.do?uri=%2Fsys_email_list.do%3Fsysparm_userpref_module%3D0271bb720a0a0b610089873ececf22c4%26sysparm_view%3Doutbox%26sysparm_query%3Dmailbox%3Doutbox%5Esys_created_onONToday@javascript:gs.daysAgoStart(0)@javascript:gs.daysAgoEnd(0)%5EEQ%26sysparm_clear_stack%3Dtrue
6.	Wait 7 Minutes for an email to be created with the subject: ${number} - Application for ${short_description} reminder
7.	Wait 28 minutes for an email to be created with the subject: ${number} - Application for ${short_description} may be withdrawn
8.	Wait 31 minutes and navigate back to the original record and watch the status is changed to ‘Withdrawn’
